overview: As the finale to Fashion Month, the Labyrinth Runway Finale is a TikTok LIVE fashion spectacular, showcasing the latest collections from renowned Black designers Victor Glemaud and Carrots by Anwar Carrots, and TikTok creator Joe Ando, hosted by Frankie Jonas with musical performances by Khalid, CL, and Lubalin.
title: TikTok’s Labyrinth Runway Finale
